      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just looking at some photos of deep space and it hit me... nothing i do actually matters. like, even if i spent my whole life trying to be \"good\" or \"successful,\" the sun is gonna explode anyway and everything just resets to zero. it feels like we're just glitches in a void that doesn't even care we exist. how can anyone even bother to keep going when the end result is just total nothingness?",
