      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"finding meaning\" in being insignificant just feels like a coping mechanism, doesnt it? like we're just lying to ourselves so we don't freak out. if the universe is truly indifferent, then our pain, our joy, our struggles... they aren't even real in any meaningful sense. it just feels like we're dragging out a sentence that was meant to be one word long.",
